{"tid":1546054,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Please delete telegram chat history before day dream","createTime":"2019-09-06T06:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T17:49:13.000Z","uid":127929,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ee5baab768e8c58045908098c1e80297f744a64f","tid":1546054,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:38:44.000Z","msg":"That would be useful and safe your life in case you are<span style=\"color: red;\"> being tracked by someone</span> (e.g. POPO)<br />\n<br />\nAlso, remember to <span style=\"color: red;\">select &quot;also delete for him/her&quot;</span> when you are deleting unwanted chat<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t6PEMb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft6PEMb4.jpg&h=82d32d60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFor more safety, please go to telegram website to <span style=\"color: red;\">remove your current account and create a new one</span>(Optional) if you have too many day dream before. (Remember to delete chat)<br />\n<br />\nLast but not least, please set Telegram auto delete account when NOT online for 1 month, and follow below security measures:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/06/143056_8c0b565e97742957dbf0d74993ab14e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F06%2F143056_8c0b565e97742957dbf0d74993ab14e6.jpg&h=91c29171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nimage source:appledaily hk"},{"pid":"1b25be10e5d3a098801d1e08236f035ab9b40aa3","tid":1546054,"uid":76702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:39:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9e4399ed417df168040950eb41e7f9717504a0c","tid":1546054,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"Share this post to save your friend"},{"pid":"de82508aa05e010d81441b96ecfa52cdd9e3aa65","tid":154605